data.description: HOME for THE HOLIDAYS! This beautiful five-bedroom, three-bathroom home on a corner lot in the lovely family-friendly Pecan Ridge neighborhood is the perfect place to create memories that will last a lifetime. From the moment you walk in, you'll feel the comfort of this home. As you enter, you will notice the open-concept floor plan that includes a nice dining area and a spacious living room that has a fireplace. The kitchen has a brand-new backsplash and stainless steel appliances. Next, you will find an office space that could also be used for a laundry room. Next, you will see the master bedroom with its own custom-made closet and private bathroom. There are also two additional bedrooms and another full bathroom on this level. Just beyond the staircase, you will find two additional bedrooms and a full bathroom. The fenced backyard has a covered patio, storage room, and plenty of space to relax and enjoy. In addition, this home has a two-car garage and a driveway. Don’t hesitate to make this your home. Please schedule a showing today!
